OL,3,C'Responsible' owner of XL bully dog
OL,4,Cshot dead by police sentenced
OL,6,FThe owner of an XL bully who branded
OL,7,Farmed police "murderers" after her dog
OL,8,Fwas shot dead has been sentenced.
OL,10,FA court heard Sophie Zaherali, 31, led
OL,11,Fa "campaign of abuse" on social media
OL,12,Fafter her dog Ghost was killed amid
OL,13,Fconcerns it was a threat the the
OL,14,Fpublic in Sheffield.
OL,16,FShe was convicted of sending malicious
OL,17,Fcommunications and owning a dog that
OL,18,Fwas dangerously out of control.
