OL,3,C'Responsible' owner of XL bully dog
OL,4,Cshot dead by police sentenced
OL,6,FBut a district judge described her as
OL,7,Fa "responsible" owner who had the
OL,8,F"lowest level of culpability" as he
OL,9,Fsentenced Zaherali to a #100 fine and
OL,10,Fa rehabilitation order.
OL,12,FSpeaking to media outside Sheffield
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court, she said she was
OL,14,F"really happy" with the sentence.
OL,16,FThe court heard Ghost escaped
OL,17,FZaherali's property onto Dunella
OL,18,FStreet in Hillsborough on 7 December
OL,19,Flast year after Zaherali tried to
OL,20,Fclose her front door, which had a
OL,21,Ffaulty lock.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
