OL,3,C'Responsible' owner of XL bully dog
OL,4,Cshot dead by police sentenced
OL,6,FShe was dealing with a medical
OL,7,Fincident involving her son at the time.
OL,9,FWhen police were called one officer,
OL,10,Freferred to as A35, fired three shots,
OL,11,Fkilling the dog "to end and mitigate
OL,12,Fthe risk it posed to the public", the
OL,13,Fcourt heard.
OL,15,FDistrict Judge Tim Spruce said
OL,16,FZaherali then carried out a "campaign
OL,17,Fof abuse" on social media and
OL,18,Fattempted to identify the officer
OL,19,Finvolved.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
