OL,3,C'Responsible' owner of XL bully dog
OL,4,Cshot dead by police sentenced
OL,6,FHe added: "The problem with social
OL,7,Fmedia is that these issues can
OL,8,Fescalate. Clearly, Zaherali had her
OL,9,Freasons, but others reading them can
OL,10,Finterpret them very differently indeed
OL,11,Fand take them too far... There is a
OL,12,Frisk to the officer and their family."
OL,14,FMr Spruce acknowledged Zaherali's
OL,15,Fbehaviour after Ghost's death was "out
OL,16,Fof character" and the result of
OL,17,F"grief".
OL,19,FHe said there was "no suggestion that
OL,20,FGhost was behaving dangerously" when
OL,21,Fofficers found him, Mr Spruce said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
