OL,3,C'Responsible' owner of XL bully dog
OL,4,Cshot dead by police sentenced
OL,6,FBut the armed officer had to rely on
OL,7,Freports of incidents involving an XL
OL,8,Fbully "potentially capable" of causing
OL,9,Fharm. The dog ran towards him when he
OL,10,Ffired the fatal shots.
OL,12,FZaherali "wasn't anything other than a
OL,13,Fresponsible owner", the district judge
OL,14,Fadded.
OL,16,FGhost was exempt from the ban on XL
OL,17,Fbully dogs and was neutered and
OL,18,Fmicrochipped, the court heard.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
