OL,3,C'Responsible' owner of XL bully dog
OL,4,Cshot dead by police sentenced
OL,6,FMr Spruce added: "A unique set of
OL,7,Fcircumstances meant that Ghost got
OL,8,Floose and left the address. She was
OL,9,Ftending to her son with autism and
OL,10,Fepilepsy. She was preoccupied, and the
OL,11,Flock on the door was faulty. It is the
OL,12,Flowest level of culpability."
OL,14,FSouth Yorkshire Police said the
OL,15,Fdecision to shoot a dog "is one never
OL,16,Ftaken lightly".
OL,18,FFirearms inspector Steve Usher said:
OL,19,F"As a dog owner you are the one
OL,20,Fresponsible for your dog's actions and
OL,21,Fthe harm or fear they cause.
