OL,3,C'Responsible' owner of XL bully dog
OL,4,Cshot dead by police sentenced
OL,6,F"To be a dog owner is a role of great
OL,7,Fresponsibility and the consequences of
OL,8,Fslack ownership can be catastrophic.
OL,10,F"Sadly, across South Yorkshire we have
OL,11,Fexperienced fatal dog attacks, and we
OL,12,Fmake no apologies that our priority
OL,13,Fwill always be the safety of the
OL,14,Fpublic and our officers.
OL,16,F"For over a year, officers have faced
OL,17,Fsignificant challenges during the
OL,18,Finvestigation and court hearings into
OL,19,FGhost and Zaherali's actions."
